data.description: Motivated Seller! 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home with fenced yard and screened 6ft deep and 19x12 pool.Pool was resurfaced in 2020, comes with an updated pool pump, heater and sweeper. Home includes tankless water heater, and new roof in 2020. HVAC is only 5 years old which is wifi equipped and can be controlled with your phone and has double paned windows as well as an updated 150 amp electrical system.  Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this beach themed home awaits your creative touch to transform it into your own dream haven.
